OL,3,CMillions missing out on energy savings
OL,4,Cas Ofgem price cap falls
OL,6,FAs July get underway, so does a new
OL,7,Fenergy price cap - with a drop in
OL,8,Fcharges of #129 on a typical bill.
OL,10,FHowever, experts are warning that
OL,11,Fmillions are missing out on much
OL,12,Fbigger savings.
OL,14,FResearch given to ITV News by Uswitch
OL,15,Fsays households could save up to #145
OL,16,Fmore, by moving to a fixed price
OL,17,Ftariff.
