OL,3,CMillions missing out on energy savings
OL,4,Cas Ofgem price cap falls
OL,6,FThe price cap sets a maximum level for
OL,7,Fenergy per kilowatt. It affects 35
OL,8,Fmillion customers who are on default
OL,9,Ftariffs, which usually means they have
OL,10,Fnever switched from their legacy
OL,11,Fsupplier.
OL,13,FThe price drop brings a typical annual
OL,14,Fbill to #1,720 for those on price
OL,15,Fcapped deals.
OL,17,FAlthough the reduction is welcome, it
OL,18,Fis still #152 a year higher than this
OL,19,Ftime in 2024.
