OL,4,Cas Ofgem price cap falls
OL,6,FITV News spoke to Emily Seymour, an
OL,7,Fenergy expert with the consumer group
OL,8,FWhich?
OL,10,FShe told us: "Summer could be a good
OL,11,Ftime to shop around for fixed deals.
OL,12,F"We'd recommend looking for deals
OL,13,Fcheaper than the price cap, not longer
OL,14,Fthan 12 months and without significant
OL,15,Fexit fees".
