OL,3,CMillions missing out on energy savings
OL,4,Cas Ofgem price cap falls
OL,6,FWith tensions in the Middle East,
OL,7,Fthere are predictions that prices will
OL,8,Frise again this winter. So, despite
OL,9,FJuly's moderate price fall, the energy
OL,10,Fcrisis continues for millions.
OL,12,FThe energy price cap for the next
OL,13,Fquarter will be published by Ofgem on
OL,14,F27 August 2025.
